    "description": "<strong>在低多边形3D风格的呈现下 ，扮演夺命辣妹，横扫僵尸大军！《热血》以八九十年代的动作大片作为灵感，是一款基于物理原理的街头打斗游戏。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/ef5ca0404c325e826e2bbcd55672571d.poster.avif?t=1720815986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/ef5ca0404c325e826e2bbcd55672571d.webm?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/ef5ca0404c325e826e2bbcd55672571d.mp4?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《热血》是《醉拳》创作者的又一款低多边形3D清版动作游戏，是时候再度上演一场大屠杀了！你将扮演一名时髦泼辣、爱说脏话的女主角洛克茜，当她和男朋友在商场购物时，她完全放松了警惕，就在此时，一场僵尸末日突然爆发。她能找到男朋友并活着逃出去吗？<br><br>从服装店到城市街道，《热血》为玩家带来了一种基于物理原理的打斗乐趣，不论是对于休闲式的多次重玩，还是硬核式的快速通关，都非常适合。游戏提供了大量挑战，但又不至于让人太把它们当回事。用各种热辣的服装装扮洛克茜，捡起简易武器，奋力拼杀，从成群的不死暴徒中成功突围。不光要在僵尸末日中生存下来，还要穿得美美哒！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/833d950643a6a91dad643ad8ead28843.poster.avif?t=1720815986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/833d950643a6a91dad643ad8ead28843.webm?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/833d950643a6a91dad643ad8ead28843.mp4?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏特性：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>扮演一名可爱的女孩，在僵尸大军中杀出重围！<br></li><li>体验第三人称清版格斗快感，探索低多边形的3D环境。<br></li><li>用各式各样诱人的服装个性化装扮洛克茜！<br></li><li>捡起简易武器，改变你的战斗风格。<br></li><li>享受荒唐可笑的物理引擎和时髦泼辣的语音对话带来的乐趣！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/259310cfe41e5a8a88d91f2452a4da23.poster.avif?t=1720815986\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/259310cfe41e5a8a88d91f2452a4da23.webm?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2129090/extras/259310cfe41e5a8a88d91f2452a4da23.mp4?t=1720815986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
